Package org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.cache.idmapping.string

Class IntTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.cache.idmapping.string.AbstractTracker<IntArray>
      • org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.cache.idmapping.string.IntTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Tracker, MemoryStatsVisitor.Visitable
    public class IntTracker
extends AbstractTracker<IntArray>
    Tracker capable of keeping int range values, using IntArray. Will fail in set(long, long) with ArithmeticException if trying to put a too big value.
